       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6BO03.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-OWNERSHIP.
           05  WS-ENTITLEMENT-PCT    PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-EXCESS-PCT         PIC S9(3)V99 VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-BO-FLAG            PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-ENTITLEMENT-PCT
           PERFORM 2200-COMPUTE-BO-MARGIN
           DISPLAY WS-BO-FLAG
           STOP RUN.
       2200-COMPUTE-BO-MARGIN.
           COMPUTE WS-EXCESS-PCT = WS-ENTITLEMENT-PCT - 15
           IF WS-EXCESS-PCT > ZERO
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-BO-FLAG
           ELSE
              MOVE 'N' TO WS-BO-FLAG
           END-IF.
